{
  "stem": "8252.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now I, at that point, it wouldn't happen very often, except, for example, for a railroad man who would pass by and who would give us a pinch and you could say hello and goodbye to him.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the next-- the next type of work that I was doing, the next camp, we-- we-- I working in a-- in a barn, with-- taking care of cows for a whole winter.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had to deal with the priests there because that were church goods-- the priest, and the people who work for the priest, and the other people, the civilians who were taking care of the land, and so on.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was just one of the workers there, talking to them, eating at the same table.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were eating there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to go to sleep in our little camp where they put us in some big barn or something, not in anybody's home.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we ate-- the-- the few of us who were assigned to that particular farm-- this was a church farm-- we ate at the table with the workers there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this is the next camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After-- after the Traunstein, which was pretty hard, but was all right, I-- I started working pretty well as the physical worker.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So one day, all of a sudden, they transfer us to Austria, Krems an der Donau, which was the other 17B, I think-- Stalag 17B-- and send us to work in Herzogenburg, Austria.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Herzogenburg was a small town, and I was still with the Polish prisoners of war there.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
